docs.text: Welcome to MkDocs For full documentation visit mkdocs.org . Commands mkdocs new [dir-name] - Create a new project. mkdocs serve - Start the live-reloading docs server. mkdocs build - Build the documentation site. mkdocs -h - Print help message and exit. Project layout mkdocs.yml # The configuration file. docs/ index.md # The documentation homepage. ... # Other markdown pages, images and other files. Coding block test #include <stdio.h> #include <stdlib.h> int main(int argc, char **argv) { int *p_int = (int *)malloc(10 * sizeof(int)); free(p_int); return 0; }
